{
  "video_id": "RlQEoJaLQRA",
  "title": "The three ways that good design makes you happy | Don Norman",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 14160.0,
      "text": "The new me is beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14160.0,
      "end_time": 15160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15160.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "Yeah, people used to say, \"Norman's OK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 22160.0,
      "text": "but if you followed what he said, everything would be usable"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 24160.0,
      "text": "but it would be ugly.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24160.0,
      "end_time": 26160.0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't have that in mind, so ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29160.0,
      "end_time": 31160.0,
      "text": "This is neat."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31160.0,
      "end_time": 33160.0,
      "text": "Thank you for setting up my display."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33160.0,
      "end_time": 35160.0,
      "text": "I mean, it's just wonderful."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35160.0,
      "end_time": 38160.0,
      "text": "And I haven't the slightest idea of what it does or what it's good for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38160.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "but I want it."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40160.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "And that's my new life."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 46160.0,
      "text": "My new life is trying to understand what beauty is about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46160.0,
      "end_time": 48160.0,
      "text": "and \"pretty,\" and \"emotions.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48160.0,
      "end_time": 52160.0,
      "text": "The new me is all about making things kind of neat and fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52160.0,
      "end_time": 56160.0,
      "text": "And so this is a Philippe Starck juicer, produced by Alessi."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56160.0,
      "end_time": 60839.0,
      "text": "It's just neat; it's fun. It's so much fun I have it in my house --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60880.0,
      "end_time": 63880.0,
      "text": "but I have it in the entryway, I don't use it to make juice."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63880.0,
      "end_time": 65880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65880.0,
      "end_time": 69880.0,
      "text": "In fact, I bought the gold-plated special edition"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69880.0,
      "end_time": 71880.0,
      "text": "and it comes with a little slip of paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71880.0,
      "end_time": 74880.0,
      "text": "that says, \"Don't use this juicer to make juice.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74880.0,
      "end_time": 77880.0,
      "text": "The acid will ruin the gold plating."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77880.0,
      "end_time": 78880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78880.0,
      "end_time": 80880.0,
      "text": "So actually, I took a carton of orange juice"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80880.0,
      "end_time": 82880.0,
      "text": "and I poured it in the glass to take this picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82880.0,
      "end_time": 85880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85880.0,
      "end_time": 87880.0,
      "text": "Beneath it is a wonderful knife."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87880.0,
      "end_time": 90880.0,
      "text": "It's a Global cutting knife made in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90880.0,
      "end_time": 95390.0,
      "text": "First of all, look at the shape -- it's just wonderful to look at."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95800.0,
      "end_time": 98800.0,
      "text": "Second of all, it's really beautifully balanced:"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98800.0,
      "end_time": 99440.0,
      "text": "it holds well, it feels well."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99480.0,
      "end_time": 101480.0,
      "text": "And third of all, it's so sharp, it just cuts."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 101480.0,
      "end_time": 103480.0,
      "text": "It's a delight to use."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103480.0,
      "end_time": 105480.0,
      "text": "And so it's got everything, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105480.0,
      "end_time": 107480.0,
      "text": "It's beautiful and it's functional."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107480.0,
      "end_time": 109480.0,
      "text": "And I can tell you stories about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109480.0,
      "end_time": 111480.0,
      "text": "which makes it reflective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111480.0,
      "end_time": 113480.0,
      "text": "and so you'll see I have a theory of emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113480.0,
      "end_time": 115480.0,
      "text": "And those are the three components."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 115480.0,
      "end_time": 118480.0,
      "text": "Hiroshi Ishii and his group at the MIT Media Lab"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118480.0,
      "end_time": 121480.0,
      "text": "took a ping-pong table and placed a projector above it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121480.0,
      "end_time": 124480.0,
      "text": "and on the ping-pong table they projected an image of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124480.0,
      "end_time": 126480.0,
      "text": "with fish swimming in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126480.0,
      "end_time": 129480.0,
      "text": "And as you play ping-pong, whenever the ball hits part of the table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 129479.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131480.0,
      "text": "the ripples spread out and the fish run away."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 131480.0,
      "end_time": 133480.0,
      "text": "But of course, then the ball hits the other side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 133480.0,
      "end_time": 136480.0,
      "text": "the ripples hit the -- poor fish, they can't find any peace and quiet."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136480.0,
      "end_time": 137480.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 137480.0,
      "end_time": 139480.0,
      "text": "Is that a good way to play ping-pong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 139480.0,
      "end_time": 141480.0,
      "text": "No. But is it fun?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 141480.0,
      "end_time": 144480.0,
      "text": "Yeah! Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 144480.0,
      "end_time": 146480.0,
      "text": "Or look at Google."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 146480.0,
      "end_time": 151480.0,
      "text": "If you type in, oh say, \"emotion and design,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 151480.0,
      "end_time": 153480.0,
      "text": "you get 10 pages of results."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 153480.0,
      "end_time": 156480.0,
      "text": "So Google just took their logo and they spread it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 156480.0,
      "end_time": 158480.0,
      "text": "Instead of saying, \"You got 73,000 results."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 158480.0,
      "end_time": 160480.0,
      "text": "This is one through 20. Next,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 160480.0,
      "end_time": 162519.0,
      "text": "they just give you as many o's as there are pages."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162520.0,
      "end_time": 164520.0,
      "text": "It's really simple and subtle."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 164520.0,
      "end_time": 167520.0,
      "text": "I bet a lot of you have seen it and never noticed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167520.0,
      "end_time": 169520.0,
      "text": "That's the subconscious mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169520.0,
      "end_time": 171520.0,
      "text": "that sort of notices it -- it probably is kind of pleasant"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 171520.0,
      "end_time": 173520.0,
      "text": "and you didn't know why."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 173520.0,
      "end_time": 175520.0,
      "text": "And it's just clever."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175520.0,
      "end_time": 177520.0,
      "text": "And of course, what's especially good is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 177520.0,
      "end_time": 179520.0,
      "text": "if you type \"design and emotion,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 179520.0,
      "end_time": 183520.0,
      "text": "the first response out of those 10 pages is my website."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 183520.0,
      "end_time": 185520.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 185520.0,
      "end_time": 188520.0,
      "text": "Now, the weird thing is Google lies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 188520.0,
      "end_time": 190520.0,
      "text": "because if I type \"design and emotion,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 190520.0,
      "end_time": 193520.0,
      "text": "it says, \"You don't need the 'and.' We do it anyway.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 193520.0,
      "end_time": 195520.0,
      "text": "So, OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 195520.0,
      "end_time": 197520.0,
      "text": "So I type \"design emotion\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 197520.0,
      "end_time": 199520.0,
      "text": "and my website wasn't first again."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 199520.0,
      "end_time": 201520.0,
      "text": "It was third."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 201520.0,
      "end_time": 203520.0,
      "text": "Oh well, different story."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 204240.0,
      "end_time": 207240.0,
      "text": "There was this wonderful review in The New York Times"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207240.0,
      "end_time": 209240.0,
      "text": "about the MINI Cooper automobile."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 209240.0,
      "end_time": 212520.0,
      "text": "It said, \"You know, this is a car that has lots of faults."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 212520.0,
      "end_time": 214520.0,
      "text": "Buy it anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 214520.0,
      "end_time": 216520.0,
      "text": "It's so much fun to drive.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 216520.0,
      "end_time": 219520.0,
      "text": "And if you look at the inside of the car --"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 219520.0,
      "end_time": 221520.0,
      "text": "I mean, I loved it, I wanted to see it, I rented it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 221520.0,
      "end_time": 224520.0,
      "text": "this is me taking a picture while my son is driving --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 224520.0,
      "end_time": 227520.0,
      "text": "and the inside of the car, the whole design is fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 227520.0,
      "end_time": 229520.0,
      "text": "It's round, it's neat."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 229520.0,
      "end_time": 231520.0,
      "text": "The controls work wonderfully."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 231520.0,
      "end_time": 234520.0,
      "text": "So that's my new life; it's all about fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 234520.0,
      "end_time": 237520.0,
      "text": "I really have the feeling that pleasant things work better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 237520.0,
      "end_time": 240520.0,
      "text": "and that never made any sense to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 240520.0,
      "end_time": 242520.0,
      "text": "until I finally figured out -- look ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 244520.0,
      "end_time": 246520.0,
      "text": "I'm going to put a plank on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 246520.0,
      "end_time": 249520.0,
      "text": "So, imagine I have a plank about two feet wide and 30 feet long"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 249520.0,
      "end_time": 252520.0,
      "text": "and I'm going to walk on it, and you see I can walk on it without looking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 252520.0,
      "end_time": 254520.0,
      "text": "I can go back and forth and I can jump up and down."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 254520.0,
      "end_time": 256519.0,
      "text": "No problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 256519.0,
      "end_time": 260519.0,
      "text": "Now I'm going to put the plank 300 feet in the air --"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 260519.0,
      "end_time": 263520.0,
      "text": "and I'm not going to go near it, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 265800.0,
      "end_time": 267800.0,
      "text": "Intense fear paralyzes you."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 267800.0,
      "end_time": 270800.0,
      "text": "It actually affects the way the brain works."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 270800.0,
      "end_time": 274800.0,
      "text": "So, Paul Saffo, before his talk said that he didn't really have it down"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 274800.0,
      "end_time": 276800.0,
      "text": "until just a few days or hours before the talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 276800.0,
      "end_time": 280800.0,
      "text": "and that anxiety was really helpful in causing him to focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 280800.0,
      "end_time": 282800.0,
      "text": "That's what fear and anxiety does;"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 282800.0,
      "end_time": 285800.0,
      "text": "it causes you to be -- what's called depth-first processing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 285800.0,
      "end_time": 288800.0,
      "text": "to focus, not be distracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 288800.0,
      "end_time": 291800.0,
      "text": "And I couldn't force myself across that."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291800.0,
      "end_time": 294800.0,
      "text": "Now some people can -- circus workers, steel workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294800.0,
      "end_time": 296800.0,
      "text": "But it really changes the way you think."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296800.0,
      "end_time": 299800.0,
      "text": "And then, a psychologist, Alice Isen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299800.0,
      "end_time": 301800.0,
      "text": "did this wonderful experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301800.0,
      "end_time": 303800.0,
      "text": "She brought students in to solve problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 303800.0,
      "end_time": 305800.0,
      "text": "So, she'd bring people into the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 305800.0,
      "end_time": 307800.0,
      "text": "and there'd be a string hanging down here"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 307800.0,
      "end_time": 309800.0,
      "text": "and a string hanging down here."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 309800.0,
      "end_time": 312800.0,
      "text": "It was an empty room, except for a table with a bunch of crap on it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 312800.0,
      "end_time": 314800.0,
      "text": "some papers and scissors and stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 314800.0,
      "end_time": 316800.0,
      "text": "And she'd bring them in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 316800.0,
      "end_time": 318800.0,
      "text": "and she'd say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 318800.0,
      "end_time": 321800.0,
      "text": "\"This is an IQ test and it determines how well you do in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 321800.0,
      "end_time": 324800.0,
      "text": "Would you tie those two strings together?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 324800.0,
      "end_time": 327800.0,
      "text": "So they'd take one string and they'd pull it over here"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 327800.0,
      "end_time": 330800.0,
      "text": "and they couldn't reach the other string."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 330800.0,
      "end_time": 332800.0,
      "text": "Still can't reach it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 332800.0,
      "end_time": 335800.0,
      "text": "And, basically, none of them could solve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 335800.0,
      "end_time": 338800.0,
      "text": "You bring in a second group of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 338800.0,
      "end_time": 341800.0,
      "text": "and you say, \"Oh, before we start,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 341800.0,
      "end_time": 344800.0,
      "text": "I got this box of candy, and I don't eat candy."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 344800.0,
      "end_time": 346800.0,
      "text": "Would you like the box of candy?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 346800.0,
      "end_time": 349800.0,
      "text": "And turns out they liked it, and it made them happy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 349800.0,
      "end_time": 351800.0,
      "text": "not very happy, but a little bit of happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 351800.0,
      "end_time": 353800.0,
      "text": "And guess what -- they solved the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 353800.0,
      "end_time": 356800.0,
      "text": "And it turns out that when you're anxious"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 356800.0,
      "end_time": 359800.0,
      "text": "you squirt neural transmitters in the brain, which focuses you"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 359800.0,
      "end_time": 361800.0,
      "text": "makes you depth-first."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 361800.0,
      "end_time": 364800.0,
      "text": "And when you're happy -- what we call positive valence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 364800.0,
      "end_time": 366800.0,
      "text": "you squirt dopamine into the prefrontal lobes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 366800.0,
      "end_time": 368800.0,
      "text": "which makes you a breadth-first problem solver:"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 368800.0,
      "end_time": 371800.0,
      "text": "you're more susceptible to interruption; you do out-of-the-box thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 371800.0,
      "end_time": 374800.0,
      "text": "That's what brainstorming is about, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 374800.0,
      "end_time": 377800.0,
      "text": "With brainstorming we make you happy, we play games,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 377800.0,
      "end_time": 379800.0,
      "text": "and we say, \"No criticism,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 379800.0,
      "end_time": 381800.0,
      "text": "and you get all these weird, neat ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 381800.0,
      "end_time": 384800.0,
      "text": "But in fact, if that's how you always were you'd never get any work done"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 384800.0,
      "end_time": 387800.0,
      "text": "because you'd be working along and say, \"Oh, I got a new way of doing it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 387800.0,
      "end_time": 391800.0,
      "text": "So to get work done, you've got to set a deadline, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 391800.0,
      "end_time": 393800.0,
      "text": "You've got be anxious."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 393800.0,
      "end_time": 395800.0,
      "text": "The brain works differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 395800.0,
      "end_time": 398800.0,
      "text": "if you're happy. Things work better because you're more creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 398800.0,
      "end_time": 401800.0,
      "text": "You get a little problem, you say, \"Ah, I'll figure it out.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 401800.0,
      "end_time": 403800.0,
      "text": "No big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 403800.0,
      "end_time": 407200.0,
      "text": "There's something I call the visceral level of processing, and there will be visceral-level design."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 407240.0,
      "end_time": 411240.0,
      "text": "Biology -- we have co-adapted through biology to like bright colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 411240.0,
      "end_time": 415240.0,
      "text": "That's especially good that mammals and primates like fruits"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 415240.0,
      "end_time": 417240.0,
      "text": "and bright plants, because you eat the fruit"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 417240.0,
      "end_time": 419240.0,
      "text": "and you thereby spread the seed."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 419240.0,
      "end_time": 422240.0,
      "text": "There's an amazing amount of stuff that's built into the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 422240.0,
      "end_time": 425240.0,
      "text": "We dislike bitter tastes, we dislike loud sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 425240.0,
      "end_time": 427240.0,
      "text": "we dislike hot temperatures, cold temperatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 427240.0,
      "end_time": 431240.0,
      "text": "We dislike scolding voices. We dislike frowning faces;"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 431240.0,
      "end_time": 433240.0,
      "text": "we like symmetrical faces, etc., etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 435640.0,
      "end_time": 437640.0,
      "text": "So that's the visceral level."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 437640.0,
      "end_time": 440640.0,
      "text": "In design, you can express visceral in lots of ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 440640.0,
      "end_time": 445640.0,
      "text": "like the choice of type fonts and the red for hot, exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 445640.0,
      "end_time": 447640.0,
      "text": "Or the 1963 Jaguar:"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 447640.0,
      "end_time": 450640.0,
      "text": "It's actually a crummy car, falls apart all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 450640.0,
      "end_time": 452640.0,
      "text": "but the owners love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 452640.0,
      "end_time": 454640.0,
      "text": "And it's beautiful -- it's in the Museum of Modern Art."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 454640.0,
      "end_time": 456640.0,
      "text": "A water bottle:"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 456640.0,
      "end_time": 459640.0,
      "text": "You buy it because of the bottle, not because of the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 459640.0,
      "end_time": 462640.0,
      "text": "And when people are finished, they don't throw it away."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 462640.0,
      "end_time": 465640.0,
      "text": "They keep it for -- you know, it's like the old wine bottles, you keep it for decoration"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 465640.0,
      "end_time": 468640.0,
      "text": "or maybe fill it with water again, which proves it's not the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 468640.0,
      "end_time": 472640.0,
      "text": "It's all about the visceral experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 473360.0,
      "end_time": 477360.0,
      "text": "The middle level of processing is the behavioral level"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 477360.0,
      "end_time": 479360.0,
      "text": "and that's actually where most of our stuff gets done."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 479360.0,
      "end_time": 481360.0,
      "text": "Visceral is subconscious, you're unaware of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 481360.0,
      "end_time": 484360.0,
      "text": "Behavioral is subconscious, you're unaware of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 484360.0,
      "end_time": 486360.0,
      "text": "Almost everything we do is subconscious."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 486360.0,
      "end_time": 490360.0,
      "text": "I'm walking around the stage -- I'm not attending to the control of my legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 490360.0,
      "end_time": 493360.0,
      "text": "I'm doing a lot; most of my talk is subconscious;"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 493360.0,
      "end_time": 495360.0,
      "text": "it has been rehearsed and thought about a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 495360.0,
      "end_time": 497360.0,
      "text": "Most of what we do is subconscious."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 497360.0,
      "end_time": 500360.0,
      "text": "Automatic behavior -- skilled behavior -- is subconscious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 500360.0,
      "end_time": 502360.0,
      "text": "controlled by the behavioral side."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 502360.0,
      "end_time": 506360.0,
      "text": "And behavioral design is all about feeling in control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 506360.0,
      "end_time": 509360.0,
      "text": "which includes usability, understanding --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 509360.0,
      "end_time": 511360.0,
      "text": "but also the feel and heft."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 511360.0,
      "end_time": 513360.0,
      "text": "That's why the Global knives are so neat."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 513360.0,
      "end_time": 515360.0,
      "text": "They're so nicely balanced, so sharp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 515360.0,
      "end_time": 517360.0,
      "text": "that you really feel you're in control of the cutting."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 517360.0,
      "end_time": 520400.0,
      "text": "Or, just driving a high-performance sports car"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 520440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522440.00000000006,
      "text": "over a demanding curb --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 522440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525440.0,
      "text": "again, feeling that you are in complete control of the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 525440.0,
      "end_time": 527440.0,
      "text": "Or the sensual feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 527440.0,
      "end_time": 529440.0,
      "text": "This is a Kohler shower, a waterfall shower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 529440.0,
      "end_time": 532440.0,
      "text": "and actually, all those knobs beneath are also showerheads."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 532440.0,
      "end_time": 534440.0,
      "text": "It will squirt you all around"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 534440.0,
      "end_time": 536440.0,
      "text": "and you can stay in that shower for hours --"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 536440.0,
      "end_time": 538440.0,
      "text": "and not waste water, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 538440.0,
      "end_time": 540440.0,
      "text": "because it recirculates the same dirty water."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 540440.0,
      "end_time": 543440.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 543440.0,
      "end_time": 545440.0,
      "text": "Or this -- this is a really neat teapot I found"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 545440.0,
      "end_time": 549440.0,
      "text": "at high tea at The Four Seasons Hotel in Chicago."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 549440.0,
      "end_time": 551440.0,
      "text": "It's a Ronnefeldt tilting teapot."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 551440.0,
      "end_time": 553440.0,
      "text": "That's kind of what the teapot looks like"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 553440.0,
      "end_time": 557680.0,
      "text": "but the way you use it is you lay it on its back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 557720.0,
      "end_time": 559720.0,
      "text": "and you put tea in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 559720.0,
      "end_time": 561720.0,
      "text": "and then you fill it with water."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 561720.0,
      "end_time": 564720.0,
      "text": "The water then seeps over the tea."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 564720.0,
      "end_time": 567720.0,
      "text": "And the tea is sitting in this stuff to the right --"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 567720.0,
      "end_time": 569720.0,
      "text": "the tea is to the right of this line."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 569720.0,
      "end_time": 571720.0,
      "text": "There's a little ledge inside, so the tea is sitting there"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 571720.0,
      "end_time": 573720.0,
      "text": "and the water is filling it up like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 573720.0,
      "end_time": 576720.0,
      "text": "And when the tea is ready, or almost ready, you tilt it."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 576720.0,
      "end_time": 579720.0,
      "text": "And that means the tea is partially covered"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 579720.0,
      "end_time": 581720.0,
      "text": "while it completes the brewing."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 581720.0,
      "end_time": 583720.0,
      "text": "And when it's finished, you put it vertically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 583720.0,
      "end_time": 585720.0,
      "text": "and now the tea is -- you remember -- above this line"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 585720.0,
      "end_time": 588720.0,
      "text": "and the water only comes to here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 588720.0,
      "end_time": 590720.0,
      "text": "and so it keeps the tea out."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 590720.0,
      "end_time": 592720.0,
      "text": "On top of that, it communicates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 592720.0,
      "end_time": 594720.0,
      "text": "which is what emotion does."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 594720.0,
      "end_time": 597720.0,
      "text": "Emotion is all about acting; emotion is really about acting."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 597720.0,
      "end_time": 599720.0,
      "text": "It's being safe in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 599720.0,
      "end_time": 603720.0,
      "text": "Cognition is about understanding the world, emotion is about interpreting it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 603720.0,
      "end_time": 605720.0,
      "text": "saying good, bad, safe, dangerous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 605720.0,
      "end_time": 608720.0,
      "text": "and getting us ready to act, which is why the muscles tense or relax."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 608720.0,
      "end_time": 612720.0,
      "text": "And that's why we can tell the emotion of somebody else --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 612720.0,
      "end_time": 614720.0,
      "text": "because their muscles are acting, subconsciously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 614720.0,
      "end_time": 620720.0,
      "text": "except that we've evolved to make the facial muscles really rich with emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 620720.0,
      "end_time": 622720.0,
      "text": "Well, this has emotions if you like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 622720.0,
      "end_time": 626720.0,
      "text": "because it signals the waiter that, \"Hey, I'm finished. See -- upright.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 626720.0,
      "end_time": 629720.0,
      "text": "And the waiter can come by and say, \"Would you like more water?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 629720.0,
      "end_time": 631720.0,
      "text": "It's kind of neat. What a wonderful design."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 631720.0,
      "end_time": 635720.0,
      "text": "And the third level is reflective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 635720.0,
      "end_time": 639720.0,
      "text": "which is, if you like the superego,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 639720.0,
      "end_time": 642720.0,
      "text": "it's a little part of the brain that has no control over what you do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 642720.0,
      "end_time": 646720.0,
      "text": "no control over the -- doesn't see the senses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 646720.0,
      "end_time": 648720.0,
      "text": "doesn't control the muscles."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 648720.0,
      "end_time": 650720.0,
      "text": "It looks over what's going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 650720.0,
      "end_time": 652720.0,
      "text": "It's that little voice in your head"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 652720.0,
      "end_time": 654720.0,
      "text": "that's watching and saying, \"That's good. That's bad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 654720.0,
      "end_time": 656720.0,
      "text": "Or, \"Why are you doing that? I don't understand.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 656720.0,
      "end_time": 660200.0,
      "text": "It's that little voice in your head that's the seat of consciousness."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 660240.0,
      "end_time": 663240.0,
      "text": "Here's a great reflective product."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 663240.0,
      "end_time": 667240.0,
      "text": "Owners of the Hummer have said, \"You know I've owned many cars in my life --"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 667240.0,
      "end_time": 669240.0,
      "text": "all sorts of exotic cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 669240.0,
      "end_time": 672240.0,
      "text": "but never have I had a car that attracted so much attention.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 673840.0,
      "end_time": 678880.0,
      "text": "It's about attention. It's about their image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 678920.0,
      "end_time": 680920.0,
      "text": "not about the car."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 680920.0,
      "end_time": 682920.0,
      "text": "If you want a more positive model --"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 682920.0,
      "end_time": 684920.0,
      "text": "this is the GM car."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 684920.0,
      "end_time": 686920.0,
      "text": "And the reason you might buy it now is because you care about the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 686920.0,
      "end_time": 688920.0,
      "text": "And you'll buy it to protect the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 688920.0,
      "end_time": 691920.0,
      "text": "even though the first few cars are going to be really expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 691920.0,
      "end_time": 693920.0,
      "text": "and not perfected."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 693920.0,
      "end_time": 695920.0,
      "text": "But that's reflective design as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 695920.0,
      "end_time": 697920.0,
      "text": "Or an expensive watch, so you can impress people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 697920.0,
      "end_time": 700920.0,
      "text": "\"Oh gee, I didn't know you had that watch.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 700920.0,
      "end_time": 702920.0,
      "text": "As opposed to this one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 702920.0,
      "end_time": 704920.0,
      "text": "which is a pure behavioral watch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 704920.0,
      "end_time": 707920.0,
      "text": "which probably keeps better time than the $13,000 watch I just showed you."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 707920.0,
      "end_time": 709920.0,
      "text": "But it's ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 709920.0,
      "end_time": 711920.0,
      "text": "This is a clear Don Norman watch."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 711920.0,
      "end_time": 714920.0,
      "text": "And what's neat is sometimes you pit one emotion against the other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 714920.0,
      "end_time": 717920.0,
      "text": "the visceral fear of falling"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 717920.0,
      "end_time": 722920.0,
      "text": "against the reflective state saying, \"It's OK. It's OK. It's safe. It's safe.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 722920.0,
      "end_time": 726920.0,
      "text": "If that amusement park were rusty and falling apart, you'd never go on the ride."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 726920.0,
      "end_time": 729920.0,
      "text": "So, it's pitting one against the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 732000.0,
      "end_time": 735000.0,
      "text": "The other neat thing ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 735000.0,
      "end_time": 739000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 739000.0,
      "end_time": 742000.0,
      "text": "So Jake Cress is this furniture maker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 742000.0,
      "end_time": 745000.0,
      "text": "and he makes this unbelievable set of furniture."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 745000.0,
      "end_time": 747000.0,
      "text": "And this is his chair with claw,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 747000.0,
      "end_time": 750000.0,
      "text": "and the poor little chair has lost its ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 750000.0,
      "end_time": 753000.0,
      "text": "and it's trying to get it back before anybody notices."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 754000.0,
      "end_time": 758000.0,
      "text": "And what's so neat about it is how you accept that story."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 758000.0,
      "end_time": 761000.0,
      "text": "And that's what's nice about emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 761000.0,
      "end_time": 763000.0,
      "text": "So that's the new me."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 763000.0,
      "end_time": 765000.0,
      "text": "I'm only saying positive things from now on."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 765000.0,
      "end_time": 766000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 766000.0,
      "end_time": 769000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}